race.description: Sdra Country Championships At Wagga Feb 28 Handicap
race.comment: BELNERA (8) has struck winning form, making it two on the bounce here last time when arriving just in time. If she can utilise the draw this time, she'll bring up the hat-trick. BONNIE MURRINGO (2) warmed nicely to ger task late when resuming here, powering late to get within a length of the winner. Will relish the added trip, though will likely be coming from a long way back at the turn. DIAMOND FROST (7) has hit the line nicely in his two runs back and will be sharpened by the blinkers going on first time. Draws well for Heywood and is a genuine threat. MENZAH ONE (3) couldn't hold off BELNERA here last time and will find it tough to turn the tables meeting her worse at the weights, but deserves respect.
